{"tid":773962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"車廂自製毒氣室　男子留書自殺昏迷","createTime":"2018-08-10T03:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T05:16:35.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"32ad00fb90aeccc9b15e60edb7e13fe8f55ba42f","tid":773962,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180810/photo/bkn-20180810073701929-0810_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180810103654\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180810%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180810073701929-0810_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180810103654&h=7ecf9a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車內留有字條。(張世洋攝)<br />\n<br />\n今日(10日)早上7時許，秀茂坪寶達邨多層停車場，有保安員巡邏期間發現一輛本田私家車引擎開動一段時間，唯私家車未有離去，保安上前查看，赫見一名男子躺臥在司機位上，而車尾排氣喉接駁一條膠管直入車廂，疑有人自製毒氣室自殺。保安員敲打車窗但男子已沒有反應，大驚下立即報警，消防及救護員趕至，將昏迷司機救出送院。<br />\n<br />\n警員在場調查，在車上發現一張疑似遺書的字條，內容寫上「原諒我的軟弱 十分累了 愛你們的每個」，警方正設法聯絡事主親友，了解其尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，駁排氣喉自殺車廂內會充斥一氧化碳，因而中毒窒息。廢氣中的一氧化碳會隨著血紅素帶到身體各處，只要濃度夠高會令人出現窒息情況，幾分鐘便可令腦部受損，10多分鐘便有機會導致死亡。如若遇到此情況欲施以援手，應在確保自己安全的情況下，打開車窗使空氣流通，或將事主搬離車廂，然後立即召救護車前來協助。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180810/bkn-20180810073701929-0810_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180810%2Fbkn-20180810073701929-0810_00822_001.html&d=0QVthNlhK99TeRNrWxp4kDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b11620c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180810/bkn-20180810073701929-0810_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0b6c331a898c124a73fe7a4c88e4ade561a63359","tid":773962,"uid":181797,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"有冇死?"},{"pid":"014b660df9199d06d5532a939a757883d5dd057d","tid":773962,"uid":88887,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:25:57.000Z","msg":"渣ga🙈"},{"pid":"27975c9fcac9950d02a3fa8533800154859024eb","tid":773962,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:06:15.000Z","msg":"係屋邨停車場實有看更睇到架喎<br />\n真係要自尋短見既點解唔去荒山野嶺呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076f4bad2bcc2437fd7cb8760b66da403da389da","tid":773962,"uid":4213,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:02:40.000Z","msg":"呢啲自殺方式咪幾好<br />\n好過啲垃圾跳樓跳車軌自焚果類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd636394105047a25a44790f2a3de235a11fd8c","tid":773962,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"連登神探召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fb9798aa43273404755f99c332ecf156591283","tid":773962,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b6c331a898c124a73fe7a4c88e4ade561a63359","tid":773962,"uid":181797,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"有冇死?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cc71f5b0efeca8e52fa1c6a06e6d9892e0282c","tid":773962,"uid":49575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6fd636394105047a25a44790f2a3de235a11fd8c","tid":773962,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"連登神探召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"有可疑! <br />\n個看更好有可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"h